These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, nurse, paramedic, pilot, security-guard
There 6 different types of food: lettuce, kiwi, cauliflower, pepper, pear, strawberry
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the lawyer##1
 2. the manager is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 3. the manager is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
 4. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the nurse##8
 5. the security-guard is somewhere to the right of the person eating pear##5
 6. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person eating cauliflower and the security-guard##7
 7. the lawyer is not to the left of the person eating cauliflower##8
 8. the pilot is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left or right of the pilot##3
10. the person eating lettuce is not to the left of the paramedic##8
11. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the paramedic##5
12. the manager is on the right of the paramedic##1
13. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the person eating cauliflower##5
14. the security-guard is somewhere between the person eating kiwi and the nurse##7
15. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
16. the pilot is not the person eating pepper##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Job           | paramedic | manager | lawyer | pilot | security-guard | nurse |
| Food   | lettuce | cauliflower    | kiwi  | pear  | pepper            | strawberry  |

