.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing, baking, woodworking, puzzles, hiking
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, cricket, sailing, soccer, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's sport is cricket##7
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
15. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
16. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##8
17. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
18. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
19. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
