.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-4::.
There 6 different types of food: eggplant, pineapple, pomegranate, radish, tomato, zucchini
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, 7up, fanta
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 3. the person eating zucchini is between the person drinking milk and the person eating eggplant##2
 4. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
 5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person drinking coffee##7
 6. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 8. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
 9. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5
11. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
12. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person eating zucchini##7
13. the person drinking fanta is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
14. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
15. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
16. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
17. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person eating zucchini##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |      6      |
| Food    | eggplant | zucchini    | tomato     | radish  | pineapple    | pomegranate |
| Beverage   | coffee  | 7up | milk | fanta | iced-tea | hot-chocolate     |

