 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person who's sport is climbing##7
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 7. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 8. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
10. the owner of the horse is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
13. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Sport   | climbing | badminton | cricket  | snowboarding     | sailing | surfing |
| Pet           | cat        | goat    | turtle | chinchilla | horse     | hamster  |

