 6. the person drinking 7up is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 8. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 9. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
